quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  69,35,"Giɗo alana ɗum ɗo hannde."
  69,36,"Wonaa ñaamde, si wonaa e ƴiƴƴiƴiri"."
  69,37,"Ñaamata ndin, si wonaa bakkondinɓe ɓeen"."
  69,38,"Mi wooɗndirii ko nji'oton kon,"
  69,39,"E ko on nji'ataa kon,"
  69,40,"won'de pellet, [Alqur'aana] ko konngol nulaaɗo tedduɗo,"
  69,41,"wonaa nde konnguɗi yimoowo; kono famɗii ko ngooŋɗinton."
  69,42,"wonaa kadi nde konnguɗi bileejo, kono famɗii ko mbaajitotoɗon."
  69,43,"ko jippinaande immi e Jeyɗo einndere nde."
  69,44,"Si tawno o fekindino e amen yoga e konnguɗi,"
  69,45,"ko pellet, min nanngirayno mo doole."
  69,46,"Hooti Min taƴayno e makko ɗaɗol ɓernde ngol."
  69,47,"Alaa e mo'on hay gooto kaɗoowo Min e makko."
  69,48,"Pellet, nde [Alqur'aanaare] konde baajitorgol gooɗuɓe ɓen."
  69,49,"Haray kadi, Miɗen nganndi ina e mon yeddooɓe [nde] ."
  69,50,"ko pellet noon, ɗuum ko nimse e hoore yedduɓe ɓeen."
  69,51,"pellet kadi, ko nde goonga jananaaɗo."
  69,52,"Haray subbunhinor innde Joom maa, mawɗo on!"
  70,1,"Torotooɗo toriima lepte janatɗe,"
  70,2,"wonan'de he'eferɓe ɓen, alaa duñanoowo ɓe ɗe,"
  70,3,"ko immorde e Allah, joom ƴawruɗe."
  70,4,"Maleykaaji wond'ude e Jibriilu hiɗi ƴawa fa'ade e makko, e ndeer ñalaande nde eɓɓoore mum woni duuɓi ujune cappanɗe jowi."
  70,5,"Muñño tan, muñal labangal."
  70,6,"Kamɓe heɓe nji'a (lepte) ɗen ko goɗɗuɗe."
  70,7,"Miɗen nji'a ɗe minen ko ɓadiiɗe,"
  70,8,"Ñande kammu nguun wa'oyta wa ko taaynaa."
  70,9,"pelle ɗeen mba'oya wa hottolle kardaako,"
  70,10,"ka ɓadondiraaɗo laɓdotaako fii jeydaaɗo mum,"